Free Trips!
Win a free trip, or get closer to flying for
free, when you surf and shop on the
Northwest Airlines WorldVacations" web site.
Trip Giveaways
Every month we give away air and hotel for two to one of
the many sublime vacation destinations we offer. Check the
web site each month to see where you could win a trip!
2,500 Bonus Miles
Book your vacation online and each person will earn an
additional 2,500 WorldPerks® Bonus Miles just for booking one
of our qualifying destinations online. Add that to the 500 to 2,000
WorldPerks Bonus Miles you receive with each World Vacations
package, plus the miles you get for flying Northwest Airlines and
you'll be that much closer to a free flight later on.
Planning Your Vacation
Whether you're just in the planning stages or ready to
book, make sure to check out our web site. We offer all
the information you need to plan and book your vacation
with a few clicks of your mouse.
WorldVacations packages are available to just about
anywhere you'd like to go:
Asia
